end Earth against waves of alien attackers. Will you choose the agile tank, capable of quick dodges and fast attacks, or the slower one with a stronger cannon? As you progress, the invaders become faster and more challenging, pushing your reflexes to the limit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Pick one of 2 tanks for defending Earth:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170700/extras/b518d146b291cc3c435ecfb8502fb040.poster.avif?t=1756730936\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170700/extras/b518d146b291cc3c435ecfb8502fb040.webm?t=1756730936\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2170700/extras/b518d146b291cc3c435ecfb8502fb040.mp4?t=1756730936\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Have fun blasting through asteroids, crushing bricks, and saving Earth from alien invasions in this tiny arcade collection!</strong></p>",
